# =========================================================================
# STARGATE FRONTEND ENVIRONMENT VARIABLES
# =========================================================================
#
# | Variable                     | Type              | Default                 | Usage / Description                                                                                                   |
# | :--------------------------- | :---------------- | :---------------------- | :-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
# | NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL          | string (URL)      | http://localhost:3001   | Base API URL for backend calls. Used in lib/api.ts and lib/sse.ts for server-sent events.                             |
# | NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL          | string (URL)      | http://localhost:3000   | Public-facing URL of the frontend. Used in developer tools page (app/dashboard/developers/page.tsx) for demo webhooks.|
# | NEXT_PUBLIC_STELLAR_NETWORK  | testnet / mainnet | testnet                 | Specifies the target Stellar network environment for transaction signing and Horizon endpoints.                       |
#
# WARNING: Never put secrets here. NEXT_PUBLIC_* variables are exposed to the browser.
# =========================================================================

NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://localhost:3001
NEXT_PUBLIC_STELLAR_NETWORK=testnet
NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL=http://localhost:3000
